Package: judgement
Type: Package
Title: SIBYL LLM Layer - Adjustment Proposals and Projection Descriptions
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The LLM-facing layer of SIBYL. propose_adjustments() translates
    a narrative into structured add-factor proposals on MARTIN equations,
    with rationales. describe_projection() drafts prose describing how a
    solved projection differs from baseline. Uses ellmer with structured
    outputs via type_object(). Defines the adjustment S3 class used as the
    contract between humans LLMs and MARTIN.
